  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether Etodalac, Etoricoxib and Dexamethasone are
      effective for Prevention of Pain ,Swelling and Trismus Following Third Molar Surgery
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
